newsitem.title: UK: UK meals and feeds mixed on quiet market.
newsitem.headline: UK meals and feeds mixed on quiet market.

text.p: Brokers on the UK meals and feeds market reported little activity and mixed sellers on Friday.
"With Chicago closed for the Independence Day all most people are thinking of is going home," said one.
High protein soymeal sellers were unchanged to two stg down ex-mill while store were 0.50 stg up.
Rapemeal from the Erith mill was one stg up while material from Liverpool and Hull was unchanged.
Sunflower meal and pellets and corn gluten feed pellets were all unchanged.
